  <tag k="charge:description" v="£1.65 for each 30 minute ride. Day Pass for £3.50 (unlimited 60-minute rides;£1 extra for each e-bike ride). Monthly membership for £20 which offers unlimited rides up to 60 minutes for 30 days."/>
